<sect1>
	<title>Creating a New Contact</title>
<para>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="blankpage.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>To create a new contact tap on the blank page icon.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Under the work tab you can enter in all relative contact information for the individuals work.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Under the work tab you can enter in all relative contact information for the individuals home.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Under the other tab you can add the individuals birthday and photograph.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Under the notes tab you can add whatever you like about the contact as well defining cagegories..</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Tap "Save" to save your contact.</para></listitem>
</orderedlist>
