<sect1>
	<title>Locating your contact in the database</title>
<para>
This Function is in the main application screen
<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>To find your contact in the listing tap in the first letter of the first name. Then tap on your contacts name to view the information in contact information at the bottom of the program.</para></listitem>
</orderedlist>
