<sect1>
	<title>Changing the program configuration</title>
<para>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="properties.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
The program configuration menu can be found by tapping the properties icon (see icon above) at the top of the main application window. You can then:
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create a new tab in the contact creation form like the location or notes category.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Create a new group for that selected tab.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Create a new field of input for the selected tab.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Delete the selected tab/field.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Optimize the database</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
Under the Categories tab you can create a category for your contact to fall under, as mentioned in "creating a new contact".
